  * src/framework/mlt_properties.c, src/framework/mlt_property.c: Use
  LC_NUMERIC_MASK instead of LC_NUMERIC in querylocale()  Without this,
  mlt_properties_set_lcnumeric() doesn't work properly on OS X.

